Even if the official explanation\nwas an electrical short.
It took a second\nfire also started
by dubious circumstances\nin February of 2016,
almost a year later--
and here I'm standing\nin this photograph
where that second\nfire occurred--
to displace the ring of\nstreet-side merchants
shown in those previous images.
The relocated market-- designed\nas a sponge to absorb this
