The solidity of the\narchitecture camouflages
a perforated envelope\noutside and in.
But it is also the integration\nof the components from the RC
slabs--
the reinforced concrete slabs--
to the doubling of the roof\nas a cushioned thermal buffer,
to the dynamics of\npressure differentials
across the courtyard that\nembolden the atmosphere
